450

458 // should have filtered bar, but not foo

460 CheckGet(db, roptions, "bar", NULL);
461 CheckGet(db, roptions, "baz", "newbazvalue");
462
463 rocksdb_suggest_compact_range(db, "bar", 3, "foo", 3, &err);
464 GetAndCheckMetaData(db);
465 CheckNoError(err);
466
467 return db;
468}

374 rocksdb_sst_file_metadata_get_relative_filename(file_meta);
375 assert(file_name);
376 assert(strlen(file_name) > 0);
377 rocksdb_free(file_name);
378
379 size_t smallest_key_len;
380 char* smallest_key = rocksdb_sst_file_metadata_get_smallestkey(
381 file_meta, &smallest_key_len);
382 assert(smallest_key);
383 assert(smallest_key_len > 0);
384 size_t largest_key_len;
385 char* largest_key =
386 rocksdb_sst_file_metadata_get_largestkey(file_meta, &largest_key_len);
387 assert(largest_key);
388 assert(largest_key_len > 0);
389 rocksdb_free(smallest_key);
390 rocksdb_free(largest_key);
391
392 rocksdb_sst_file_metadata_destroy(file_meta);
393 }
394 assert(level_size == file_size_in_level);
395 total_level_size += level_size;
396 rocksdb_level_metadata_destroy(level_meta);
397 }
398 assert(total_file_count > 0);
399 assert(cf_size == total_level_size);
400}

1082 rocksdb_sstfilewriter_finish(writer, &err);
1083 CheckNoError(err);
1084
1085 rocksdb_ingestexternalfileoptions_t* ing_opt =
1086 rocksdb_ingestexternalfileoptions_create();
1087 const char* file_list[1] = {sstfilename};
1088 rocksdb_ingest_external_file(db, file_list, 1, ing_opt, &err);
1089 CheckNoError(err);
1090 CheckGet(db, roptions, "sstk1", "v1");
1091 CheckGet(db, roptions, "sstk2", "v2");
1092 CheckGet(db, roptions, "sstk3", "v3");
1093
1094 remove(sstfilename);
1095 rocksdb_sstfilewriter_open(writer, sstfilename, &err);
1096 CheckNoError(err);
1097 rocksdb_sstfilewriter_put(writer, "sstk2", 5, "v4", 2, &err);
1098 CheckNoError(err);
1099 rocksdb_sstfilewriter_put(writer, "sstk22", 6, "v5", 2, &err);
1100 CheckNoError(err);
1101 rocksdb_sstfilewriter_put(writer, "sstk3", 5, "v6", 2, &err);
1102 CheckNoError(err);
1103 rocksdb_sstfilewriter_finish(writer, &err);
1104 CheckNoError(err);
1105
1106 rocksdb_ingest_external_file(db, file_list, 1, ing_opt, &err);
1107 CheckNoError(err);
1108 CheckGet(db, roptions, "sstk1", "v1");
1109 CheckGet(db, roptions, "sstk2", "v4");
1110 CheckGet(db, roptions, "sstk22", "v5");
1111 CheckGet(db, roptions, "sstk3", "v6");
1112
1113 rocksdb_sstfilewriter_open(writer, sstfilename, &err);
1114 CheckNoError(err);
1115 rocksdb_sstfilewriter_put(writer, "abc1", 4, "v7", 2, &err);
1116 CheckNoError(err);
1117 rocksdb_sstfilewriter_put(writer, "abc2", 4, "v8", 2, &err);
1118 CheckNoError(err);
1119 rocksdb_sstfilewriter_put(writer, "abc3", 4, "v9", 2, &err);
1120 CheckNoError(err);
1121 rocksdb_sstfilewriter_put(writer, "abc4", 4, "v10", 3, &err);
1122 CheckNoError(err);
1123 rocksdb_sstfilewriter_delete_range(writer, "abc1", 4, "abc4", 4, &err);
1124 CheckNoError(err);
1125 rocksdb_sstfilewriter_finish(writer, &err);
1126 CheckNoError(err);

1128 rocksdb_ingestexternalfileoptions_destroy(ing_opt);
1129 rocksdb_sstfilewriter_destroy(writer);
1130 rocksdb_envoptions_destroy(env_opt);

1133 rocksdb_delete(db, woptions, "sstk1", 5, &err);

1136 CheckNoError(err);
1137 rocksdb_delete(db, woptions, "sstk22", 6, &err);
1138 CheckNoError(err);
1139 rocksdb_delete(db, woptions, "sstk3", 5, &err);
1140 CheckNoError(err);

1170 const char* end_list[1] = {"baz"};
1171 const size_t end_sizes[1] = {3};
1172 rocksdb_writebatch_delete_rangev(wb, 1, start_list, start_sizes, end_list,
1173 end_sizes);
1174 rocksdb_write(db, woptions, wb, &err);

1176 CheckGet(db, roptions, "bay", NULL);
1177 rocksdb_writebatch_destroy(wb);

1314 rocksdb_iter_next(iter);
1315 CheckIter(iter, "foo", "hello");
1316 rocksdb_iter_prev(iter);
1317 CheckIter(iter, "box", "c");
1318 rocksdb_iter_prev(iter);
1319 CheckCondition(!rocksdb_iter_valid(iter));
1320 rocksdb_iter_seek_to_last(iter);
1321 CheckIter(iter, "foo", "hello");
1322 rocksdb_iter_seek(iter, "b", 1);
1323 CheckIter(iter, "box", "c");
1324 rocksdb_iter_seek_for_prev(iter, "g", 1);
1325 CheckIter(iter, "foo", "hello");
1326 rocksdb_iter_seek_for_prev(iter, "box", 3);
1327 CheckIter(iter, "box", "c");
1328 rocksdb_iter_get_error(iter, &err);
1329 CheckNoError(err);
1330 rocksdb_iter_destroy(iter);

1385 StartPhase("approximate_sizes");
1386 {
1387 int i;
1388 int n = 20000;
1389 char keybuf[100];
1390 char valbuf[100];
1391 uint64_t sizes[2];
1392 const char* start[2] = {"a", "k00000000000000010000"};
1393 size_t start_len[2] = {1, 21};
1394 const char* limit[2] = {"k00000000000000010000", "z"};
1395 size_t limit_len[2] = {21, 1};
1396 rocksdb_writeoptions_set_sync(woptions, 0);
1397 for (i = 0; i < n; i++) {
1398 snprintf(keybuf, sizeof(keybuf), "k%020d", i);
1399 snprintf(valbuf, sizeof(valbuf), "v%020d", i);
1400 rocksdb_put(db, woptions, keybuf, strlen(keybuf), valbuf, strlen(valbuf),
1401 &err);
1402 CheckNoError(err);
1403 }
1404 rocksdb_approximate_sizes(db, 2, start, start_len, limit, limit_len, sizes,
1405 &err);
1406 CheckNoError(err);
1407 CheckCondition(sizes[0] > 0);
1408 CheckCondition(sizes[1] > 0);
1409 }
1410
1411 StartPhase("property");
1412 {
1413 char* prop = rocksdb_property_value(db, "nosuchprop");
1414 CheckCondition(prop == NULL);
1415 prop = rocksdb_property_value(db, "rocksdb.stats");
1416 CheckCondition(prop != NULL);
1417 Free(&prop);
1418 }
1419
1420 StartPhase("snapshot");
1421 {
1422 const rocksdb_snapshot_t* snap;
1423 snap = rocksdb_create_snapshot(db);
1424 rocksdb_delete(db, woptions, "foo", 3, &err);
1425 CheckNoError(err);
1426 rocksdb_readoptions_set_snapshot(roptions, snap);
1427 CheckGet(db, roptions, "foo", "hello");
1428 rocksdb_readoptions_set_snapshot(roptions, NULL);
1429 CheckGet(db, roptions, "foo", NULL);
1430 rocksdb_release_snapshot(db, snap);
1431 }
1432 StartPhase("snapshot_with_memtable_inplace_update");
1433 {
1434 rocksdb_close(db);
1435 const rocksdb_snapshot_t* snap = NULL;
1436 const char* s_key = "foo_snap";
1437 const char* value1 = "hello_s1";
1438 const char* value2 = "hello_s2";
1439 rocksdb_options_set_allow_concurrent_memtable_write(options, 0);
1440 rocksdb_options_set_inplace_update_support(options, 1);
1441 rocksdb_options_set_error_if_exists(options, 0);
1442 db = rocksdb_open(options, dbname, &err);
1443 CheckNoError(err);
1444 rocksdb_put(db, woptions, s_key, 8, value1, 8, &err);
1445 snap = rocksdb_create_snapshot(db);
1446 assert(snap != NULL);
1447 rocksdb_put(db, woptions, s_key, 8, value2, 8, &err);
1448 CheckNoError(err);
1449 rocksdb_readoptions_set_snapshot(roptions, snap);
1450 CheckGet(db, roptions, "foo", NULL);
1451 // snapshot syntax is invalid, because of inplace update supported is set
1452 CheckGet(db, roptions, s_key, value2);
1453 // restore the data and options
1454 rocksdb_delete(db, woptions, s_key, 8, &err);
1455 CheckGet(db, roptions, s_key, NULL);
1456 rocksdb_release_snapshot(db, snap);
1457 rocksdb_readoptions_set_snapshot(roptions, NULL);
1458 rocksdb_options_set_inplace_update_support(options, 0);
1459 rocksdb_options_set_allow_concurrent_memtable_write(options, 1);
1460 rocksdb_options_set_error_if_exists(options, 1);
1461 }
1462 StartPhase("repair");
1463 {
1464 // If we do not compact here, then the lazy deletion of
1465 // files (https://reviews.facebook.net/D6123) would leave
1466 // around deleted files and the repair process will find
1467 // those files and put them back into the database.
1468 rocksdb_compact_range(db, NULL, 0, NULL, 0);
1469 rocksdb_close(db);
1470 rocksdb_options_set_create_if_missing(options, 0);
1471 rocksdb_options_set_error_if_exists(options, 0);
1472 rocksdb_options_set_wal_recovery_mode(options, 2);
1473 rocksdb_repair_db(options, dbname, &err);
1474 CheckNoError(err);
1475 db = rocksdb_open(options, dbname, &err);
1476 CheckNoError(err);
1477 CheckGet(db, roptions, "foo", NULL);
1478 CheckGet(db, roptions, "bar", NULL);
1479 CheckGet(db, roptions, "box", "c");
1480 rocksdb_options_set_create_if_missing(options, 1);
1481 rocksdb_options_set_error_if_exists(options, 1);
1482 }
1483
1484 StartPhase("filter");
1485 for (run = 1; run <= 4; run++) {
1486 // run=0 uses custom filter (not currently supported)
1487 // run=1 uses old block-based bloom filter
1488 // run=2 run uses full bloom filter
1489 // run=3 uses Ribbon
1490 // run=4 uses Ribbon-Bloom hybrid configuration
1491 CheckNoError(err);
1492 rocksdb_filterpolicy_t* policy;
1493 if (run == 1) {
1494 policy = rocksdb_filterpolicy_create_bloom(8.0);
1495 } else if (run == 2) {
1496 policy = rocksdb_filterpolicy_create_bloom_full(8.0);
1497 } else if (run == 3) {
1498 policy = rocksdb_filterpolicy_create_ribbon(8.0);
1499 } else {
1500 policy = rocksdb_filterpolicy_create_ribbon_hybrid(8.0, 1);
1501 }
1502 rocksdb_block_based_options_set_filter_policy(table_options, policy);
1503 rocksdb_block_based_options_set_optimize_filters_for_memory(table_options,
1504 0);
1505
1506 // Create new database
1507 rocksdb_close(db);
1508 rocksdb_destroy_db(options, dbname, &err);
1509 rocksdb_options_set_block_based_table_factory(options, table_options);
1510 db = rocksdb_open(options, dbname, &err);
1511 CheckNoError(err);
1512 rocksdb_put(db, woptions, "foo", 3, "foovalue", 8, &err);
1513 CheckNoError(err);
1514 rocksdb_put(db, woptions, "bar", 3, "barvalue", 8, &err);
1515 CheckNoError(err);
1516
1517 {
1518 // Add enough keys to get just one reasonably populated Bloom filter
1519 const int keys_to_add = 1500;
1520 int i;
1521 char keybuf[100];
1522 for (i = 0; i < keys_to_add; i++) {
1523 snprintf(keybuf, sizeof(keybuf), "yes%020d", i);
1524 rocksdb_put(db, woptions, keybuf, strlen(keybuf), "val", 3, &err);
1525 CheckNoError(err);
1526 }
1527 }
1528 rocksdb_compact_range(db, NULL, 0, NULL, 0);
1529
1530 CheckGet(db, roptions, "foo", "foovalue");
1531 CheckGet(db, roptions, "bar", "barvalue");
1532
1533 {
1534 // Query some keys not added to identify Bloom filter implementation
1535 // from false positive queries, using perfcontext to detect Bloom
1536 // filter behavior
1537 rocksdb_perfcontext_t* perf = rocksdb_perfcontext_create();
1538 rocksdb_perfcontext_reset(perf);
1539
1540 const int keys_to_query = 10000;
1541 int i;
1542 char keybuf[100];
1543 for (i = 0; i < keys_to_query; i++) {
1544 snprintf(keybuf, sizeof(keybuf), "no%020d", i);
1545 CheckGet(db, roptions, keybuf, NULL);
1546 }
1547
1548 const int hits =
1549 (int)rocksdb_perfcontext_metric(perf, rocksdb_bloom_sst_hit_count);
1550 if (run == 0) {
1551 // Due to half true, half false with fake filter result
1552 CheckCondition(hits == keys_to_query / 2);
1553 } else if (run == 1 || run == 2 || run == 4) {
1554 // For run == 1, block-based Bloom is no longer available in public
1555 // API; attempting to enable it enables full Bloom instead.
1556 //
1557 // Essentially a fingerprint of full Bloom schema, format_version=5
1558 CheckCondition(hits == 188);
1559 } else {
1560 // Essentially a fingerprint of Ribbon schema
1561 CheckCondition(hits == 226);
1562 }
1563 CheckCondition(
1564 (keys_to_query - hits) ==
1565 (int)rocksdb_perfcontext_metric(perf, rocksdb_bloom_sst_miss_count));
1566
1567 rocksdb_perfcontext_destroy(perf);
1568 }
1569
1570 // Reset the policy
1571 rocksdb_block_based_options_set_filter_policy(table_options, NULL);
1572 rocksdb_options_set_block_based_table_factory(options, table_options);
1573 }
1574
1575 StartPhase("compaction_filter");
1576 {
1577 rocksdb_options_t* options_with_filter = rocksdb_options_create();
1578 rocksdb_options_set_create_if_missing(options_with_filter, 1);
1579 rocksdb_compactionfilter_t* cfilter;
1580 cfilter = rocksdb_compactionfilter_create(NULL, CFilterDestroy,
1581 CFilterFilter, CFilterName);
1582 // Create new database
1583 rocksdb_close(db);
1584 rocksdb_destroy_db(options_with_filter, dbname, &err);
1585 rocksdb_options_set_compaction_filter(options_with_filter, cfilter);
1586 db = CheckCompaction(db, options_with_filter, roptions, woptions);
1587
1588 rocksdb_options_set_compaction_filter(options_with_filter, NULL);
1589 rocksdb_compactionfilter_destroy(cfilter);
1590 rocksdb_options_destroy(options_with_filter);
1591 }
1592
1593 StartPhase("compaction_filter_factory");
1594 {
1595 rocksdb_options_t* options_with_filter_factory = rocksdb_options_create();
1596 rocksdb_options_set_create_if_missing(options_with_filter_factory, 1);

1811 break;

1814 break;
1815 case 2:
1816 CheckEqual(NULL, vals[i], vals_sizes[i]); // normal not found
1817 break;
1818 }
1819 Free(&vals[i]);
1820 }

1831 false);

1838 rocksdb_pinnableslice_destroy(pvals[i]);

2012 CheckNoError(err);

2028 rocksdb_approximate_memory_usage_get_mem_table_unflushed(mu2) >=
2029 rocksdb_approximate_memory_usage_get_mem_table_unflushed(mu1));

2967 StartPhase("jemalloc_nodump_allocator");
2968 {
2969 rocksdb_memory_allocator_t* allocator;
2970 allocator = rocksdb_jemalloc_nodump_allocator_create(&err);
2971 if (err != NULL) {
2972 // not supported on all platforms, allow unsupported error
2973 const char* ni = "Not implemented: ";
2974 size_t ni_len = strlen(ni);
2975 size_t err_len = strlen(err);
2976
2977 CheckCondition(err_len >= ni_len);
2978 CheckCondition(memcmp(ni, err, ni_len) == 0);
2979 Free(&err);
2980 } else {
2981 rocksdb_cache_t* co;
2982 rocksdb_lru_cache_options_t* copts;
2983
2984 copts = rocksdb_lru_cache_options_create();
2985
2986 rocksdb_lru_cache_options_set_capacity(copts, 100);
2987 rocksdb_lru_cache_options_set_memory_allocator(copts, allocator);
2988
2989 co = rocksdb_cache_create_lru_opts(copts);
2990 CheckCondition(100 == rocksdb_cache_get_capacity(co));
2991
2992 rocksdb_cache_destroy(co);
2993 rocksdb_lru_cache_options_destroy(copts);
2994 }
2995 rocksdb_memory_allocator_destroy(allocator);
2996 }

3466 StartPhase("two-phase commit");
3467 {
3468 // open a TransactionDB
3469 txn_db_options = rocksdb_transactiondb_options_create();
3470 txn_options = rocksdb_transaction_options_create();
3471 rocksdb_options_set_create_if_missing(options, 1);
3472 txn_db = rocksdb_transactiondb_open(options, txn_db_options, dbname, &err);
3473 CheckNoError(err);
3474
3475 rocksdb_transaction_options_set_skip_prepare(txn_options, 0);
3476 txn = rocksdb_transaction_begin(txn_db, woptions, txn_options, NULL);
3477 rocksdb_transaction_commit(txn, &err);
3478 CheckCondition(err != NULL);
3479 Free(&err);
3480 err = NULL;
3481 rocksdb_transaction_prepare(txn, &err);
3482 CheckCondition(err != NULL);
3483 Free(&err);
3484 err = NULL;
3485 rocksdb_transaction_set_name(txn, "txn1", 4, &err);
3486 CheckNoError(err);
3487 rocksdb_transaction_prepare(txn, &err);
3488 CheckNoError(err);
3489 rocksdb_transaction_commit(txn, &err);
3490 CheckNoError(err);
3491 rocksdb_transaction_destroy(txn);
3492
3493 // prepare 2 transactions and close db.
3494 rocksdb_transaction_t* txn1 =
3495 rocksdb_transaction_begin(txn_db, woptions, txn_options, NULL);
3496 rocksdb_transaction_put(txn1, "bar1", 4, "1", 1, &err);
3497 CheckNoError(err);
3498 rocksdb_transaction_set_name(txn1, "txn1", 4, &err);
3499 CheckNoError(err);
3500 rocksdb_transaction_prepare(txn1, &err);
3501 CheckNoError(err);
3502 rocksdb_transaction_t* txn2 =
3503 rocksdb_transaction_begin(txn_db, woptions, txn_options, NULL);
3504 rocksdb_transaction_put(txn2, "bar2", 4, "2", 1, &err);
3505 CheckNoError(err);
3506 rocksdb_transaction_set_name(txn2, "txn2", 4, &err);
3507 CheckNoError(err);
3508 rocksdb_transaction_prepare(txn2, &err);
3509 CheckNoError(err);
3510 rocksdb_transaction_destroy(txn1);
3511 rocksdb_transaction_destroy(txn2);
3512 rocksdb_transactiondb_close(txn_db);
3513 rocksdb_transaction_options_destroy(txn_options);
3514 rocksdb_transactiondb_options_destroy(txn_db_options);
3515
3516 // reopen db and get all prepared.
3517 txn_db_options = rocksdb_transactiondb_options_create();
3518 txn_options = rocksdb_transaction_options_create();
3519 rocksdb_options_set_error_if_exists(options, 0);
3520 txn_db = rocksdb_transactiondb_open(options, txn_db_options, dbname, &err);
3521 CheckNoError(err);
3522 CheckTxnDBPinGet(txn_db, roptions, "bar1", NULL);
3523 CheckTxnDBPinGet(txn_db, roptions, "bar2", NULL);
3524 size_t cnt;
3525 rocksdb_transaction_t** txns =
3526 rocksdb_transactiondb_get_prepared_transactions(txn_db, &cnt);
3527 CheckCondition(cnt == 2);
3528 size_t i;
3529 for (i = 0; i < cnt; i++) {
3530 txn = txns[i];
3531 size_t name_len = 0;
3532 char* name = rocksdb_transaction_get_name(txn, &name_len);
3533 CheckCondition(name_len == 4);
3534 if (strncmp(name, "txn1", name_len) == 0) {
3535 rocksdb_transaction_commit(txn, &err);
3536 } else if (strncmp(name, "txn2", name_len) == 0) {
3537 rocksdb_transaction_rollback(txn, &err);
3538 }
3539 rocksdb_free(name);
3540 CheckNoError(err);
3541 rocksdb_transaction_destroy(txn);
3542 }
3543 rocksdb_free(txns);
3544 CheckTxnDBGet(txn_db, roptions, "bar1", "1");
3545 CheckTxnDBGet(txn_db, roptions, "bar2", NULL);
3546 rocksdb_transactiondb_put(txn_db, woptions, "bar2", 4, "2", 1, &err);
3547 CheckNoError(err);
3548
3549 // close and destroy
3550 rocksdb_transactiondb_close(txn_db);
3551 rocksdb_destroy_db(options, dbname, &err);
3552 CheckNoError(err);
3553 rocksdb_transaction_options_destroy(txn_options);
3554 rocksdb_transactiondb_options_destroy(txn_db_options);
3555 }
3556
3557 StartPhase("transactions_multi_get_for_update");
3558 {
3559 // open a TransactionDB
3560 txn_db_options = rocksdb_transactiondb_options_create();
3561 rocksdb_transactiondb_options_set_transaction_lock_timeout(txn_db_options,
3562 0);
3563 txn_options = rocksdb_transaction_options_create();
3564 rocksdb_options_set_create_if_missing(options, 1);
3565 txn_db = rocksdb_transactiondb_open(options, txn_db_options, dbname, &err);
3566 CheckNoError(err);
3567
3568 rocksdb_transactiondb_put(txn_db, woptions, "foo", 3, "hey", 3, &err);
3569 CheckNoError(err);
3570 rocksdb_transactiondb_put(txn_db, woptions, "bar", 3, "hello", 5, &err);
3571 CheckNoError(err);
3572
3573 // begin transactions
3574 txn = rocksdb_transaction_begin(txn_db, woptions, txn_options, NULL);
3575 rocksdb_transaction_t* txn2 =
3576 rocksdb_transaction_begin(txn_db, woptions, txn_options, NULL);
3577
3578 // multi get
3579 {
3580 const char* keys[2] = {"foo", "bar"};
3581 const size_t keys_sizes[2] = {3, 3};
3582 char* vals[2];
3583 size_t vals_sizes[2];
3584 char* errs[2];
3585 const char* expected[2] = {"hey", "hello"};
3586 rocksdb_transaction_multi_get_for_update(
3587 txn, roptions, 2, keys, keys_sizes, vals, vals_sizes, errs);
3588 CheckMultiGetValues(2, vals, vals_sizes, errs, expected);
3589 }
3590
3591 char* conflict_err = NULL;
3592 size_t val_len;
3593 rocksdb_transaction_get_for_update(txn2, roptions, "foo", 3, &val_len, true,
3594 &conflict_err);
3595 // get-for-update conflict
3596 CheckCondition(conflict_err != NULL);
3597 Free(&conflict_err);
3598
3599 // commit
3600 rocksdb_transaction_commit(txn, &err);
3601 CheckNoError(err);
3602
3603 // should work after first tx is commited
3604 CheckTxnGetForUpdate(txn2, roptions, "foo", "hey");
3605
3606 // commit the second one
3607 rocksdb_transaction_commit(txn2, &err);
3608 CheckNoError(err);
3609
3610 // destroy txns
3611 rocksdb_transaction_destroy(txn);
3612 rocksdb_transaction_destroy(txn2);
3613
3614 // same for column families
3615
3616 rocksdb_column_family_handle_t* cfh;
3617 cfh = rocksdb_transactiondb_create_column_family(txn_db, options,
3618 "txn_db_cf", &err);
3619 CheckNoError(err);
3620
3621 rocksdb_transactiondb_put_cf(txn_db, woptions, cfh, "cf_foo", 6, "cf_hello",
3622 8, &err);
3623 CheckNoError(err);
3624 rocksdb_transactiondb_put_cf(txn_db, woptions, cfh, "cf_bar", 6, "cf_hey",
3625 6, &err);
3626 CheckNoError(err);
3627
3628 txn = rocksdb_transaction_begin(txn_db, woptions, txn_options, NULL);
3629 txn2 = rocksdb_transaction_begin(txn_db, woptions, txn_options, NULL);
3630
3631 {
3632 const rocksdb_column_family_handle_t* get_handles[2] = {cfh, cfh};
3633 const char* keys[2] = {"cf_foo", "cf_bar"};
3634 const size_t keys_sizes[2] = {6, 6};
3635 char* vals[2];
3636 size_t vals_sizes[2];
3637 char* errs[2];
3638 const char* expected[2] = {"cf_hello", "cf_hey"};
3639 rocksdb_transaction_multi_get_for_update_cf(txn, roptions, get_handles, 2,
3640 keys, keys_sizes, vals,
3641 vals_sizes, errs);
3642 CheckMultiGetValues(2, vals, vals_sizes, errs, expected);
3643 }
3644
3645 char* conflict_err_cf = NULL;
3646 size_t val_len_cf;
3647 rocksdb_transaction_get_for_update_cf(txn2, roptions, cfh, "cf_foo", 6,
3648 &val_len_cf, true, &conflict_err_cf);
3649 CheckCondition(conflict_err_cf != NULL);
3650 Free(&conflict_err_cf);
3651
3652 rocksdb_transaction_commit(txn, &err);
3653 CheckNoError(err);
3654
3655 CheckTxnGetForUpdateCF(txn2, roptions, cfh, "cf_foo", "cf_hello");
3656
3657 rocksdb_transaction_commit(txn2, &err);
3658 CheckNoError(err);
3659
3660 // close and destroy
3661 rocksdb_column_family_handle_destroy(cfh);
3662 rocksdb_transaction_destroy(txn);
3663 rocksdb_transaction_destroy(txn2);
3664 rocksdb_transactiondb_close(txn_db);
3665 rocksdb_destroy_db(options, dbname, &err);
3666 CheckNoError(err);
3667 rocksdb_transaction_options_destroy(txn_options);
3668 rocksdb_transactiondb_options_destroy(txn_db_options);
3669 }
